title: Merry And Bright A Country Holiday Collection JediMaster
description:
New 2013 Country Christmas album ripped in high quality flac. Contains 12 tracks by various country artists.

Track List

1. Santa Claus is Coming to town (Charlie Worsham) 
2. Up on the rooftop (Rodney Atkins) 
3. O Holy Night (Lee Brice) 
4. Have Yourself a Merry Little Christmas (Jana Kramer) 
5. Run run Rudolph (Frankie Ballard) 
6. Santa Looked a lot like Daddy (Travis Tritt) 
7. Blue Christmas (Big & Rich) 
8. Rockin' Around the Christmas Tree (LeAnn Rimes) 
9. Santa Claus is Back in Town (Dwight Yoakam) 
10. I'll be home for Christmas (Craig Campbell) 
11. Mary, Did you know (Kenny Rogers and Wynonna Judd) 
12. The Christmas Song (Randy Travis) 

Merry Christmas! Enjoy.

JediMaster
